file.name: request_body_expected.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Entities
  version: "1.0"
servers:
  - url: /
paths:
  /person:
    put:
      summary: Update an existing person
      description: Update an existing person by Id
      operationId: updatePerson
      requestBody:
        description: Update an existent person in the store
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/UpdatePerson"
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful operation
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Person"
components:
  schemas:
    Person:
      required:
        - age
        - name
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        age:
          minimum: 11
          type: integer
    UpdatePerson:
      type: string
      enum:
        - a
        - b
